  <ThingDef ParentName="ArmorHelmetMakeableBase">
      <defName>Apparel_AnimalPlateArmor</defName>
      <label>animal plate armor</label>
      <description>Armor plates designed to cover a four-legged animal's body. Primitive and cumbersome, but provides effective protection against gunfire and melee attacks.\nCurrently Wearable by:\nBears, Cat, Cougar, Elephant, Husky, Labrador Retriever, Lynx, Megasloth, Panther, Rhinoceros, Thrumbo, Warg, Wild Boar, Wolves</description>
